:\"22112974\"},\"za_data\":{\"attach_info\":\"\"}}","https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/29795698":"{\"card_type\":\"card_1\",\"display\":{\"title\":\"开发笔记（一）：个人开发者的困境与突破\",\"card_open_url\":\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/29795698\",\"desc\":\"181 赞同 · 13 评论 \\u003ca class=\\\"tag type_a\\\"\\u003e文章\\u003c/a\\u003e\",\"content\":\"\\u003ca class=\\\"text normal/bold\\\" data-color=\\\"#444444\\\" data-night-color=\\\"#D3D3D3\\\"\\u003e小芋:\\u003c/a\\u003e 本文主要与大家分享我业余时间如何学习多门技术以及开发业余项目的一些心得，分为 初衷、硬技能、软技能、第一生产力、环境、时间几个部分，阅读大概需要 10 分钟。 关于我之前做的一些业余项目，我在知乎上的一个回答大概可以总结：小芋头君：作为程序员，你有哪些正在做的个人项目？ 业余开发项目的初衷总体来说，在我的感觉里，国内的环境对于业余开发者来说其实是非常不友好的，不过作为一个开发者，一味抱怨并不会有大的改观…\",\"image\":{\"image_url\":\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e07cd7f218238cc19b1290d0ace3f399_r.jpg?source=172ae18b\",\"ratio\":1,\"is_video\":false},\"bg_type\":\"dark\"},\"source\":{\"content_type\":\"ARTICLE\",\"content_id\":\"29795698\"},\"za_data\":{\"attach_info\":\"\"}}"},"matrix_tips":"45 赞同 · 65 收藏 · 5 评论","navigator_vote":false,"question":{"created":1526953443,"id":"278137232","question_type":"normal","relationship":null,"title":"搞什么副业可以月入过万？","type":"question","updated_time":1552056609,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/278137232"},"reaction_instruction":{},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"upvoted_followees":[],"voting":0},"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_text":"","relevant_type":""},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"sticky_info":"","suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"description":"","note":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"status":""},"url":""},"thanks_count":11,"thumbnail_info":{"count":0,"thumbnails":[],"type":"thumbnail_info"},"type":"answer","updated_time":1601044344,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/1474897863","visible_only_to_author":false,"vote_next_step":"vote","voteup_count":45},"skip_count":false,"position":0,"cursor":"52341586ee0d5eb70aefe3fa3db31db8","is_jump_native":false},{"type":"question_feed_card","target_type":"answer","target":{"admin_closed_comment":false,"annotation_action":null,"answer_type":"normal","attached_info":"ogEQCAQQAxje95fQCSCQk9CEAZICJQoJNDk5OTE4NTQyEgoyNTg0MDgzNDIyGAQiCklNQUdFX1RFWFQ=","author":{"avatar_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-cc605990d753afaa93b995e12b6ed94f_l.jpg?source=1def8aca","avatar_url_template":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-cc605990d753afaa93b995e12b6ed94f.jpg?source=1def8aca","badge":[],"badge_v2":{"detail_badges":[],"icon":"","merged_badges":[],"night_icon":"","title":""},"exposed_medal":{"avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c26a65592e2109d144bb55fecc48841a_l.png?source=1def8aca","description":"回答 100 个问题","medal_avatar_frame":"","medal_id":"972440607604559872","medal_name":"知无不言","mini_avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-c26a65592e2109d144bb55fecc48841a_r.png?source=1def8aca"},"follower_count":114,"gender":0,"headline":"","id":"c4a5d462d69293c197e5b8faf6b5c768","is_advertiser":false,"is_followed":false,"is_following":false,"is_org":false,"is_privacy":false,"name":"春花佳佳","type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c4a5d462d69293c197e5b8faf6b5c768","url_token":"chun-hua-jia-jia","user_type":"people"},"can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"collapse_reason":"","collapsed_by":"nobody","comment_count":5,"comment_permission":"all","content":"\u003cp data-pid=\"ftW57tYL\"\u003e作为一个刚毕业一年的打工人，我想给小伙伴们说\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"LGT8YtbZ\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e一定要学会PPT！！！真的很重要很重要很重要！！！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"iJ5J19Tt\"\u003e刚毕业的时候，我一个普通人，没什么特长，不知道做什么副业，每个月只能拿着普通的工资，过日子，想买什么东西都要想好久，买了之后又要过很久紧紧巴巴的日子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"t1ufrper\"\u003e还好做了接单PPT这个副业，不然现在还会是那样的日子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"V5BCsVKd\"\u003e这是我最近三个月的收入。（仅代表个人收益）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4d78cf1484feeadb0836909665975eed_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"345\" data-rawheight=\"231\" data-original-token=\"v2-9859453da43a02a774d9db04cfb51b15\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cb1e50870c582cabb1139d719b213ce3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"345\"/\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39; width=\u0026#39;345\u0026#39; height=\u0026#39;231\u0026#39;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"345\" data-rawheight=\"231\" data-original-token=\"v2-9859453da43a02a774d9db04cfb51b15\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cb1e50870c582cabb1139d719b213ce3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"345\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4d78cf1484feeadb0836909665975eed_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"EMoXMbIy\"\u003e我靠会做PPT，在公司得到老板的青睐，同事也开始了PPT副业，一个月轻松多了几千元的收入。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"7ST6RgGb\"\u003e这里我总结了一份10万字PPT速成接单教程，如果你也想做副业的话，那真的是你得必备之选。现在我免费分享给你\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"ad-link-card\" data-ad-id=\"Plugin_efc5ec321c8d9b9fce23fb660a9255e6\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-589538334b3a8c638ce77bfb93a27f24_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"842\" data-rawheight=\"742\" data-original-token=\"v2-0cd706230e0418abdef7c75367b7d24a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cf9557e1c7099532c2bac828a33fdc4f_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"842\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-589538334b3a8c638ce77bfb93a27f24_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39; width=\u0026#39;842\u0026#39; height=\u0026#39;742\u0026#39;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"842\" data-rawheight=\"742\" data-original-token=\"v2-0cd706230e0418abdef7c75367b7d24a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cf9557e1c7099532c2bac828a33fdc4f_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"842\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-589538334b3a8c638ce77bfb93a27f24_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-589538334b3a8c638ce77bfb93a27f24_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003ca data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"ad-link-card\" data-ad-id=\"Plugin_efc5ec321c8d9b9fce23fb660a9255e6\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"JR-Beth_\"\u003e全文还有干货分享，是我从的宝贝干货都给小伙伴们啦——PPT封面技巧，让你震惊全公司！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"t1Q2lnef\"\u003e第一步：在 PPT 中插入想要设置成背景的图片，按住【Crtl+C】复制；接着新建一张幻灯片，右键点击在空白处，在弹出框中选择【\u003cb\u003e设置背景格式\u003c/b\u003e】；然后在任务窗格中选择【\u003cb\u003e图片或纹理填充\u003c/b\u003e】——【\u003cb\u003e剪贴板\u003c/b\u003e】。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-dcbbe59546b31c8b0468897b97eb4c62_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"495\" data-rawheight=\"875\" data-original-token=\"v2-dcbbe59546b31c8b0468897b97eb4c62\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-dcbbe59546b31c8b0468897b97eb4c62_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"495\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-dcbbe59546b31c8b0468897b97eb4c62_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39; width=\u0026#39;495\u0026#39; height=\u0026#39;875\u0026#39;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"495\" data-rawheight=\"875\" data-original-token=\"v2-dcbbe59546b31c8b0468897b97eb4c62\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-dcbbe59546b31c8b0468897b97eb4c62_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"495\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-dcbbe59546b31c8b0468897b97eb4c62_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-dcbbe59546b31c8b0468897b97eb4c62_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"eL-c5RUb\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e第二步：\u003c/b\u003e在当前 PPT 中然后插入三个矩形，摆放成图中的样子；接着依次选中矩形，在【\u003cb\u003e插入形状\u003c/b\u003e】工具栏中点击【\u003cb\u003e合并形状\u003c/b\u003e】——【\u003cb\u003e拆分\u003c/b\u003e】，然后删除多余部分，保留如图所示的两个梯形。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d2b519369f1150b1137713e9734a6ea_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"495\" data-rawheight=\"875\" data-original-token=\"v2-3d2b519369f1150b1137713e9734a6ea\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d2b519369f1150b1137713e9734a6ea_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"495\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3d2b519369f1150b1137713e9734a6ea_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39; width=\u0026#39;495\u0026#39; height=\u0026#39;875\u0026#39;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"495\" data-rawheight=\"875\" data-original-token=\"v2-3d2b519369f1150b1137713e9734a6ea\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d2b519369f1150b1137713e9734a6ea_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"495\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3d2b519369f1150b1137713e9734a6ea_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d2b519369f1150b1137713e9734a6ea_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"eWWzT9D7\"\u003e第三步：选中梯形，分别再复制一个梯形并旋转 180 度，与原有的梯形摆放在一起；接着选中所有梯形，点击【\u003cb\u003e开始\u003c/b\u003e】——【\u003cb\u003e绘图\u003c/b\u003e】的右下角扩展箭头，调出【\u003cb\u003e设置形状格式\u003c/b\u003e】的任务窗格；然后选择【\u003cb\u003e填充\u003c/b\u003e】——【\u003cb\u003e幻灯片背景填充\u003c/b\u003e】。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c32a70e403dbbac38d716436e0779fec_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"492\" data-rawheight=\"879\" data-original-token=\"v2-c32a70e403dbbac38d716436e0779fec\" data-thumbnail=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c32a70e403dbbac38d716436e0779fec_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"492\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c32a70e403dbbac38d716436e0779fec_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39; width=\u0026#39;492\u0026#39; height=\u0026#39;879\u0026#39;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"492\" data-rawheight=\"879\" data-original-token=\"v2-c32a70e403dbbac38d716436e0779fec\" data-thumbnail=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c32a70e403dbbac38d716436e0779fec_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"492\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c32a70e403dbbac38d716436e0779fec_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c32a70e403dbbac38d716436e0779fec_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"cDXwsmjb\"\u003e第四步：继续设置梯形的形状格式，点击【\u003cb\u003e阴影\u003c/b\u003e】，在【\u003cb\u003e预设\u003c/b\u003e】中选择【\u003cb\u003e外部\u003c/b\u003e】——【\u003cb\u003e偏移：下\u003c/b\u003e】，其他参数设置如图所示：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b02b699aabf6dabc14cbb13bdd4a6718_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"843\" data-rawheight=\"720\" data-original-token=\"v2-463800955a88f97544c5041da0c0e7fd\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-044f1ddaed11b4968d71103c40ca3b01_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"843\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b02b699aabf6dabc14cbb13bdd4a6718_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39; width=\u0026#39;843\u0026#39; height=\u0026#39;720\u0026#39;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"843\" data-rawheight=\"720\" data-original-token=\"v2-463800955a88f97544c5041da0c0e7fd\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-044f1ddaed11b4968d71103c40ca3b01_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"843\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b02b699aabf6dabc14cbb13bdd4a6718_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b02b699aabf6dabc14cbb13bdd4a6718_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"n1V2BNZh\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e第五步：\u003c/b\u003e接下来需要添加动画，首先选中其中一个梯形，在【\u003cb\u003e动画\u003c/b\u003e】选项卡中，选择【\u003cb\u003e添加动画\u003c/b\u003e】——【\u003cb\u003e其他动作路径\u003c/b\u003e】；接着在弹出框中找到【\u003cb\u003e直线和曲线\u003c/b\u003e】——【\u003cb\u003e向左\u003c/b\u003e】；然后在【\u003cb\u003e计时\u003c/b\u003e】工具栏中设置【\u003cb\u003e持续时\u003c/b\u003e间】为「2.5s」。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a178f231ad9db2e5e3865abc5583ad6_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"492\" data-rawheight=\"879\" data-original-token=\"v2-4a178f231ad9db2e5e3865abc5583ad6\" data-thumbnail=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a178f231ad9db2e5e3865abc5583ad6_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"492\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-4a178f231ad9db2e5e3865abc5583ad6_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39; width=\u0026#39;492\u0026#39; height=\u0026#39;879\u0026#39;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"492\" data-rawheight=\"879\" data-original-token=\"v2-4a178f231ad9db2e5e3865abc5583ad6\" data-thumbnail=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a178f231ad9db2e5e3865abc5583ad6_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"492\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-4a178f231ad9db2e5e3865abc5583ad6_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4a178f231ad9db2e5e3865abc5583ad6_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"8B4LcoyS\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e第六步：\u003c/b\u003e在【\u003cb\u003e高级动画\u003c/b\u003e】工具栏中，打开【\u003cb\u003e动画窗格\u003c/b\u003e】，双击该动画，在弹出框中设置效果参数，勾选【\u003cb\u003e自动翻转\u003c/b\u003e】，最后点击【\u003cb\u003e确定\u003c/b\u003e】：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"8plauUSs\"\u003e效果参数设置：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"0JnOqPQS\"\u003e平滑开始：1.25 秒\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"uxGBlxaS\"\u003e平滑结束：1.25 秒\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"XLTDp1s8\"\u003e弹跳结束：0 秒\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-bcc59a2e77ab1c9c876f16d59560e1d5_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"492\" data-rawheight=\"879\" data-original-token=\"v2-bcc59a2e77ab1c9c876f16d59560e1d5\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-bcc59a2e77ab1c9c876f16d59560e1d5_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"492\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-bcc59a2e77ab1c9c876f16d59560e1d5_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39; width=\u0026#39;492\u0026#39; height=\u0026#39;879\u0026#39;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"492\" data-rawheight=\"879\" data-original-token=\"v2-bcc59a2e77ab1c9c876f16d59560e1d5\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-bcc59a2e77ab1c9c876f16d59560e1d5_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"492\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-bcc59a2e77ab1c9c876f16d59560e1d5_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-bcc59a2e77ab1c9c876f16d59560e1d5_720w.gif?source=1def8aca\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"Nz4hOG9R\"\u003e第七步：再次给梯形添加动画，首先选中梯形，点击【\u003cb\u003e添加动\u003c/b\u003e画】，选择【\u003cb\u003e放大/缩小\u003c/b\u003e】；